Charlotte Valandrey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlotte_Valandrey 0 Charlotte Valandrey (born 29 November 1968 in Paris, France) is a French actress. After early success she was widely tipped for stardom, but her career took a more modest course until the release of her autobiography in 2005.
